<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <meta name="description" content="See the world through my eyes!">
    <title>Portfolio</title>
    <link
      rel="stylesheet"
      as="style"
      href="style.css">
    <script
      rel="preload"
      src="index.js"
      defer></script>
  </head>
  <body>
    {% include 'head' %}

    <header>
      {% include 'nav' %}
    </header>

    {{ repos | json }}

    <ul>
      {% for repo in repos %}
        <li>
          {{ repo.name }}:
          <a href="{{ repo.html_url }}">{{ repo.html }}</a>
        </li>
      {% endfor %}
    </ul>

    <main>
      <h1>Inez <br> El Azzouzi</h1>
      <h2>Frontend Developer</h2>
      <h2>Creative Developer</h2>
      <h2>Multi-Disciplinary Artisan
      </h2>

      <p class="about" id="about">
        About me   I started programming for the first time back in 2023, having no idea what programming is.
        <br> Though, as someone who loves art, i see this as a different way to translate my creativity into code.
        <br> So i started from scratch with no knowledge.
        <br> And now, I aspire to become a Creative Developer.
      </p>

      <section class="projects" id="projects">
        <h3>I Love Web</h3>
        <h3>Creative Coding Spikes</h3>
        <h3>Three.js</h3>
        <h3>Profile Card</h3>
        <h3>Side Projects</h3>
      </section>
    </main>

    {% include 'contact' %}
  </body>
</html>

{% comment %} 
to restart the terminal:
  npx @11ty/eleventy --serve

genereerd dynamische bestanden:
  npx @11ty/eleventy
{% endcomment %}